The paper discusses the use of Genetic Programming (GP) to improve the accuracy and explainability of Machine Learning (ML) algorithms through feature construction. This topic falls under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), Data Mining (cs.DM), and Software Engineering (cs.SE) as it involves the development and optimization of algorithms for ML and AI, as well as the analysis and interpretation of data.
